=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我咪又係著salomon xa pro 3d <br />\n磨到平晒底一樣都係咁行<br />\n綑邊綑啲簡單嘅都好輕鬆<br />\n玩青山腹地嗰啲更加無問題<br />\n呢張係喺上面落嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mV1nEK2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmV1nEK2.jpg&h=a964616d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跣唔跣真係唔太關對鞋事<br />\n自己最近都買咗對5.10 stealth底<br />\n行澗同綑邊係好有用<br />\n但行其他路況 絕對係會辛苦自己<br />\n太咬地反而要用多幾錢力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7df34895e9fbfc85ac34e6cc021c9e7497c2dda","tid":1962873,"uid":255867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T10:06:18.000Z","msg":"成日見D山友落山跳下跳下好似好輕鬆咁，膝頭唔攰架咩"},{"pid":"b1aea95d3a39a70fd24d54be4f779a7ef16c81f4","tid":1962873,"uid":17319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T23:18:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"853861936fd81d77eb0f1674efc8c15f2542225a","tid":1962873,"uid":29675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T01:09:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3411288/org/d0ef5137e88dd7c54d9aca04b7b05832.jpg/W0AFXPbFutAjUBngdD7ZTDVOlcDZEZ1_2A85etgPOXo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3411288%2Forg%2Fd0ef5137e88dd7c54d9aca04b7b05832.jpg%2FW0AFXPbFutAjUBngdD7ZTDVOlcDZEZ1_2A85etgPOXo&h=91364c18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3411294/org/3b38b7701116cd9dcf4ce0b6ed522c90.jpg/1jNWFc9QagHzfLsTX8FbDhxGX3_TenYPwPKKTMDyikw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3411294%2Forg%2F3b38b7701116cd9dcf4ce0b6ed522c90.jpg%2F1jNWFc9QagHzfLsTX8FbDhxGX3_TenYPwPKKTMDyikw&